IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. EVEN-ODD-DETECTOR.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 NUMBER PIC 9(5).
01 REMAINDER PIC 9(1).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-LOGIC.
    DISPLAY "Enter a number: ".
    ACCEPT NUMBER.
    COMPUTE REMAINDER = MOD(NUMBER, 2).
    IF REMAINDER = 0 THEN
        DISPLAY NUMBER " is even."
    ELSE
        DISPLAY NUMBER " is odd."
    END-IF.
    STOP RUN.
